                                          'the special case of energy '
                                          'specified as a wavelength (via the '
                                          '"wl" source parameter), the mean '
                                          'wavelength rather than energy will '
                                          'be used where that makes a '
                                          'difference.'},
               'absorption': {'name': 'absorption',
