                                            'effects. If set to 1 (the '
                                            'default) they will be included '
                                            'implicitly through attenuation of '
                                            'neutrons weights. If set to 0, '
                                            'the absorption cross section will '
                                            'be artificially set to 0barn.'},
               'nscatlimit': {'name': 'nscatlimit',
                              'default_value': 'none',
                              'example_values': ['none',
